<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1169</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài zhè lǐ yǒu yī zuò jì tán, tán shàng yǐ yǒu liè huǒ xiǎn xiàn.
 yīn wèi shén yuè nà wǒ men bǐ cǐ xiāng ài, wǒ men zài cì bǎ quán rén fèng xiàn.
 jǔ mù kàn nà lán lán de tiān, měi lì de cǎi hóng zài tiān biān.
 shén yǔ nǐ yǔ wǒ lì xià yǒng yuǎn de yuē, tā de jiā tā bì zhào guǎn.
 shén a wǒ men yǎng wàng nǐ, yīn nǐ cháng xiàng wǒ men xiǎn xiàn.
 wǒ men de xīn zǎo yǐ jìng jìng děng hòu, zài zhè lǐ yǒu yī zuò jì tán.</lyrics>
<title>zài zhè lǐ yǒu yī zuò jì tán 迦南1169</title>
</song>